title: The Moon Lay Hidden Beneath A Cloud rest on your arms reversed
description:
THE MOON LAY HIDDEN BENEATH A CLOUD  &#039;Rest on Your Arms Reversed&#039;  CD
(1999 Arthur&#039;s Round Table/World Serpent)

17 untitled tracks from compilations, limited releases, and unreleased.

Albin Julius went on to DER BLUTHARSCH.  THE MOON LAY HIDDEN BENEATH A CLOUD had a more medieval sound.



World Serpent went out of business a few years ago.

There has been talk of reissuing the back catalog of TMLHBAC, but so far nothing has happened.
